    <refname>RFC CDK #10</refname>
  </refnamediv>

  <refsect1>
    <title>Proposal</title>
    <para>
The addition of two fields with get and set methods for storage of the 
covalent and vanderwaals radii for the atom type. 
    </para>
  </refsect1>

  <refsect1>
    <title>Reason</title>
    <para>
This is needed to move port Jmol to CDK.
    </para>
